Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾以为你是我的命中之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:50.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能比你更好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:52.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里都找不到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:56.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:01.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校要叫老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:02.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:07.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师还不是叫我小花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:12.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟从小看着你长大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:19.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钟井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:24.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆 皆川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:29.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:32.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:34.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有 有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:35.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:38.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你有东西忘在办公室了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:40.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给 文件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:42.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:43.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:53.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:55.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:57.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这上面贴满了标签一看就是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 让你见笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:03.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:05.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:07.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:12.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有回报的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:16.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那真的是很美的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不那样想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:57.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:05.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:12.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以互相替代的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是高二的开学典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 坐回位子上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:06.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我原本就知道哥哥会来学校上班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:10.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但没想到他居然会成为我们班的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:18.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以后每天都能在学校见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大致上不太擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 钟井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有学生找你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:41.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我把讲义拿来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:49.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 一直只注视着哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:54.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我比他更早地察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他露出了我从没见过的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我疏忽大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:06.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到居然被那种像是乡下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:09.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无魅力的半老徐娘抢先…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:23.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 感觉小花懂事多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:28.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是鸣海你来了才变安分的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:31.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花的妈妈很擅长料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:42.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉呀 多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今天花火也有帮忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很难得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不好意思 承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:00.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然因为这样微不足道的事就觉得得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的心情才是最无可救药的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:01.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}没事啦 自从你出去工作后不也好久没来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}改天再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:04.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然家里做的饭就是好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:13.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我家只有我和老爸两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而吃自己做的饭总觉得乏味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:18.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快点找到一个好老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哥哥的口头禅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:32.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,从他读初中的时候就在念叨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近不怎么说了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:35.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:40.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,具体的对象已经出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:50.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊小花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:51.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,第一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:55.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:59.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么花火不和爸爸妈妈一起跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊 好年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是她爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,耍赖啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:10.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,耍赖耍赖耍…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:17.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿那种鞋子才是耍赖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:25.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是超跑系列吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:30.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师明明说过不准穿到学校来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 乃莉子你又擅自
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说小花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:52.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥和小花一起跑才不是耍赖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:54.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:03.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥要吃小花妈妈做的便当也不是耍赖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:07.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈不是说有工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是她熬夜努力做出来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:12.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要好好吃别剩下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 小花真是不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老妈做的饭有多宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:31.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是哥哥你不是跟你爸爸去钓鱼什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:36.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有爸爸 所以很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:38.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:46.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小花都拥有让彼此羡慕的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:51.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才能在对方寂寞的时候帮上忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,教音乐的皆川老师真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新任教师吧 跟我们年纪差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学在盯着这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:30.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:31.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是看我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:33.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说 是在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗？没伤到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:46.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,长长的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,土得掉渣的淡茶色对襟毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像是故意要让人闻到的沐浴露的香气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恰到好处的自然妆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 小麦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:08.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是学校 皆川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:12.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是 是啊 没两下我又忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙也是这女人的粉丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}粟屋君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:20.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:24.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道那种眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:26.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:37.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那个人喜欢的对象是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:41.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:49.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐是我初中时的家庭教师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:54.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到又成了我的高中老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:58.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然当时觉得超级走运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:06.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么哥哥会觉得那女人好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:09.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂别说茜姐的坏话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是是男人就是喜欢那种像女主播一样的女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}都说叫你别说人坏话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:17.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}唉一肚子火害得我都饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}听人说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:15.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都十分执着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:20.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且思念越深
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就越是感觉到心无可依
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后意识到这个的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在一起的时间增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:39.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别湿漉漉地在别人的床上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想上学啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钟井老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那要放弃么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:55.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:09.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最初不知为何 只是打算开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:16.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:19.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 完全不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:28.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概在那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们都想着同样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:46.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把我 试着当成是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:07.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 本来麦就不喜欢我也对我没感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:11.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算是把麦当作是麦来看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不把他当麦来看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也是替身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是真想要做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你要不要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,本来你就完全不像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是任性啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明还算是比较帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛闭上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:55.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对 要做就做彻底点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像哥哥一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,指尖很冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳很聒噪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:17.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想哥哥对我这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:33.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有种触电的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:36.88,Kuzu_scene1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1089.6,522.6)\fad(400,1900)}触电的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻什么的还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:44.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:45.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:54.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只有一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,变得不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:34.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 这是哥哥的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:38.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:50.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥不会做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会对我做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:56.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:58.00,Kuzu_scene2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\t(\fs82.5)\t(1440,1940,\blur7.5)\t(1840,2357,\alpha&HFF)\move(1329.6,503.4,1351.2,501,0,2000)}摸我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.83,Kuzu_scene2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\t(\fs82.5)\t(900,1315,\blur7.5)\t(1357,1816,\alpha&HFF)\move(530.4,695.4,496.8,685.8,0,1700)}再
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.38,Kuzu_scene2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\t(\fs93)\alpha&HFF\blur7.5\t(0,730,\blur0\alpha&H00)\move(1248,381,1315.2,342.6,21,2148)}更多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.38,Kuzu_scene2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\t(\fs93)\alpha&HFF\blur7.5\t(0,730,\blur0\alpha&H00)\pos(770.4,580.2)}更多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.38,Kuzu_scene2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\t(\fs93)\alpha&HFF\blur7.5\t(0,730,\blur0\alpha&H00)\move(271.2,753,211.2,793.8,21,2190)}更多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也必须忍着不出声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让人认为这是「我」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让人认为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:26.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:33.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这就看不到脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:40.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不尽力地去回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:43.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,尽力地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:54.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs42\fn微软雅黑\b1\frz68.13\frx32\fry6\move(339.043,638.615,448.758,640.329,24,1150)}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.10,Kuzu_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H70716F&\b1\frz348.4\move(921.858,37.285,927,342.429,27,1528)}谢谢你前几天的晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.10,Kuzu_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H70716F&\b1\frz348.4\move(901.285,83.571,908.142,388.714,27,1528)}还会继续去打扰你的m(_ _)m
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.10,Kuzu_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H70716F&\b1\frz348.4\move(896.142,133.284,901.285,440.142,27,1528)}不要对班上的同学说呢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.10,Kuzu_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H70716F&\b1\frz348.4\move(872.143,181.286,880.715,484.714,27,1528)}下次把要看的书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.10,Kuzu_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H70716F&\b1\frz348.4\move(861.857,231,870.429,532.714,27,1528)}拿来给你呢{}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:05.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:10.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 虽然怎么说今天就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:21.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今后 不再做…这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:28.92,Kuzu_scene1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1111.2,299.4)\fad(1000,0)\alpha&H30}又再、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.92,Kuzu_scene1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(753.6,489)\fad(1000,0)\alpha&H30}七月——。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:32.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:33.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我好好地回应你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:38.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等了一星期才有的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 让人有期待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:54.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被没有兴趣的人告白示好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:57.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这更恶心的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自取其辱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45}boomerang
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:12.32,Kuzu_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}注：「boomerang」也就是回飞镖，暗指自己说出的话伤到自己。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:16.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没能放开手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是麦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而是想要试着通过麦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:32.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:43.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,突然来了吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为已经不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:07.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 是要交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:11.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后想要相互依靠的时候能有所偎依
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:16.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定不会万一一不小心喜欢上我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会 我确定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全不是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:29.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后 我们做了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会喜欢上彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:36.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一方成就了真正的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:38.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这段关系就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:39.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:42.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「除心以外 皆你所属」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:51.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来 我们两个人的关系是炮…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:56.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是没做吗 做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概以后也不会做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:01.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:06.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人会寂寞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相互依靠不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个果然是因为我是处女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？你突然之间说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:18.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,实现给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人渣的本愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
