Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.51,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}一番大切なものを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.98,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}一番大切にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.57,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな単純なことが今は一番出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.44,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}もしも運命があるのならば　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:49.16,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「あなたは運命の人」なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:54.00,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな言葉今を壊しそうで言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.62,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近くに居ても遠く感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.14,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}行ったり来たりしてるこの想い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.15,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}諦める　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.30,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}終わらない花占い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.74,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}宝箱の鍵失ったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:09.36,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}キラキラした想いて抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:16.90,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}仄かに色付いた欠片をため息に隠す
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.36,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}目が合ったなら逸らさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.94,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}秘められたこの嘘を見抜いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.42,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}限界がもう分からないの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.21,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}だから今は何も言わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.27,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}苦しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:46.20,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}怖いほどあなたが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.51,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.98,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最想要去珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.57,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如此简单的事情现在却最无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.44,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若是真的存在命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:49.16,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「你就是我的命定之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:54.00,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}无法说出口 惧怕这些话语将会毁掉现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.62,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近在咫尺却仿若遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.14,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}反复无常的这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.15,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}放弃 还是坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.30,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}永无止境的花瓣占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.74,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若然丢失了宝箱的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:09.36,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}抱紧最后一丝希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:16.90,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}将逐渐泛红的碎片藏进一声声叹息中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.36,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如果看着我 请不要移开目光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.94,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}让你看透我所隐藏的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.42,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}我不知自己能坚持到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.21,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}所以现在请你沉默就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.27,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}爱的如此痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:46.20,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}爱的如此恐惧
